title: Google Pixel 4 Reactions & a Chat with iJustine & Jenna Ezarik
description:
Today, we take a deep-dive into our initial thoughts on the Google launch event and the brand-new Pixel 4. We also recap several fun videos we recently published, including an interview with Will Smith and a project where we re-uploaded a video 1,000 times! Finally, we welcome tech-creator sisters Justine and Jenna Ezarik to discuss their Camera Camp and all of our hopes & dreams for the 2020 iPhone.
